Title: Implementing a Support Vector Machine E-Mail Spam Classification Filter
Slug: svm-email-filter-implementation
Date: 2016-3-31
Tags: svm, sklearn, classification
Author: David Kaleko
Summary: Inspired by a Coursera Machine Learning homework assigment, I implement a support vector machine e-mail spam classification filter. I use a dataset from the web of sample spam and non-spam e-mails and evaluate the performance of an SVM model on a test subset.
Headline: Never Get Spammed Again!